content: This game was good but was way too dark but i still enjoyed.
I like this game! It is very scary! Thou I do wish I insted bout the celler version. But it does not mater! It's still a very good game! Slender man lovers I recommend this game!
I tried the free version. It's no different from the purchased one so don't waste your money.
It's not even scary but slenderina the cellar and slenderina house are the scary ones I love this one is just boring
Very very good and really scary one of the better games on here that really does make you to afraid to turn around to see what's behind you 10/10...

My favourite horror game by far! It's great that she jumps out at you - nice touch! My only concern is that now ALL the scares seem to come from those random pop ups... There's no fear in turning around to see if she's followed you like in Slender Rise Again, which makes it less tense and less creepy. I found the pop ups made me jump less the more I played and the fear of being followed would help change that. A balance would earn this game 5 stars from me!
I don't jump very often but first time she appeared my heart started pounding. Great game with very chilling music. I like slenderman but this is better.

I have played alot of the free version of slendrina,and after playing the full game Im even more addicted!The things I love most about this game are: #1,how you actually have an objective instead of just picking up pages.#2,how slendrina is different then any monster I've seen in a mobile horror game. #3,How addicting and fun this game is! The only things I think should be changed (which I know you probably already thought of) is some sort of animation to slendrina, and a screaming sound when she see's you.
replyContent:
Hello.
Thank you so much. I am very glad that you like Slendrina. Yes i have thought about an animation on her, but im not sure yet. And a scream sound is a good idea.
/DVloper

content: Nice, controls well, sound is OK, as are the graphics. She made me jump on the first level ( the only one I've played so far), so that says something. Good job. Edit: really enjoying. One of the few slender games where you can loose. She will sometimes pop up right in front of you. Sick of all these slender games where slender is just annoyance. Good job!
